name: Hellbear Seed of Bearstruction
description:
A classic cover of the legendary Mike Minoliabear, Hellbear discovers some of the secrets of his murky purpose, and rallies against his destiny. Will he succeed in throwing off the chains of fate? or will he fulfill his destiny as bringer of the end?

You can own this Colectibear bear bearbear for the low low price of Bear
